welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Palmerston, a charming city known for its beautiful landscapes and friendly locals. We invite you to explore and experience all that our city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal at Darwin Airport, serving domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: A secondary terminal at Darwin Airport, primarily serving regional and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport, with a 2-hour time limit per session.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Delissaville Airport is a modern and spacious facility that serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Delissaville Airport is equipped to handle a wide range of cargo and freight, including perishable goods and oversized items.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport, simply connect to the network and follow the prompts to access the internet.
